AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Entry on Bourke Street	
Enter through the main entry point and continue straight. The charge point will be located to your left in a few meters.
Entry on Parlement Street	
Entry to Drostdy Hotel Parking. Continue with the road turning right, near the other exit to your right the charge point will be visible.
